stha added. \"People have started to go out for morning walk citing shops are open until nine in the morning and even started evening walk. Infection is rising. We have not been able to isolate all the infected persons.\"\n\nHe reasoned that people will be sacred to even walk outside if curfew is imposed and action can be taken against the violators.","title":"Prohibitory orders in Kathmandu Valley extended by one week","url":"http://en.setopati.com/political/153813","video":[]}
